01:17:43.659 --> 01:17:44.616
7:00 AM.

01:17:44.660 --> 01:17:48.054
[soft suspenseful music]

01:17:57.020 --> 01:17:59.413
[phone ringing]

01:18:01.111 --> 01:18:02.547
